{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "87a14940-f0dd-4415-89f0-5bd713ed28e4",
    "name": "restful-booker",
    "description": "This collection covers the core REST API endpoints for the **Restful Booker** platform — a hotel booking service commonly used for API testing and learning.\n\nIt includes the following requests:\n\n- **Health Check** — `GET /ping` verifies that the API is up and running.\n- **Authentication** — `POST /auth` generates a token required for protected operations.\n- **Create Booking** — `POST /booking` creates a new hotel booking.\n- **Get All Bookings** — `GET /booking` retrieves a list of all bookings.\n- **Get Booking by ID** — `GET /booking/:id` fetches the details of a specific booking using a dynamic `bookingId` variable.\n- **Update Booking** — `PUT /booking` fully replaces an existing booking's data.\n- **Partial Update** — `PATCH /booking` updates specific fields of an existing booking.\n- **Delete Booking** — `DELETE /booking` removes a booking from the system.\n\nThe collection uses the `base_Url`, `authToken`, and `bookingId` environment variables to keep requests flexible and environment-agnostic. Pair it with the **restful-booker** environment to get started quickly.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "55250068",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/55250068-87a14940-f0dd-4415-89f0-5bd713ed28e4?source=collection_link"
  },
